name: Flora Liang
about: Hi! I'm Flora and I'm a freshmen majoring in Applied Economics and Management with a possible minor in sustainability and fashion design. Aside from DTI, I am a Cornell Tradition Fellow and a member of Cornell Marketing, SWIB, Cornell Fashion Collective, and Thread Magazine. I am passionate about being environmentally conscious through sewing, embroidering, and upcycling thrifted clothing. Feel free to reach out!
